creator: Challingo
descriptionHtml:
Challingo is a social networking app. It is a platform for any kind of challenges which we call "chally" and you are able to actively react on them.
You can either just watch, like, share, comment or create and complete these chally. Inspire yourself in new and interesting activities.
Challenge your friends and the whole world because life itself is a big chally!
It is up to you. So let's do something!

• Watch hundreds of interesting and funny videos and photos. Inspire yourself and your followers.

• Create new viral chally

• Challenge your friends and followers

• Complete chally made by other users that you like

Do you have any new ideas or wanna share your experience? We will love your feedback! Send us anytime an e-mail at hello@challingo.com
or contact us at our Facebook - Challingo
and Instagram - Challingo_app
